11:48.932 --> 11:57.682
Do you know trees like hickory trees and long leaf pine are exceptional at we stand in the wind?

11:58.498 --> 11:59.800
I don't know that.

11:59.920 --> 12:05.247
The hickories develop in massive tap roots of over 150 feet deep.

12:06.108 --> 12:15.400
