14:18.256 --> 14:22.482
Maybe you've moved house, maybe, maybe, maybe whatever that might be.

14:27.330 --> 14:33.938
But in every case, if your roots are planted in something other than Jesus, you are actually drought stressed.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.643
Your life is actually drought stressed.

14:39.325 --> 14:42.389
And at some point, you will realize that you're not thriving.

14:43.310 --> 14:45.392
You are at best surviving without Jesus.

14:47.375 --> 14:56.306
The bottom line, this juxtaposition in Psalm 1, in fact, in the whole of scripture describes a simple choice that we all have to make.

14:56.642 --> 15:01.969
